description: This skill is created by an insurance agent to help people understand the basics of car insurance in the USA. Insurance is regulated at state level and many of the coverage limits and descriptions vary by state. The fact database will increase over time, it will include many interesting facts about teen driving and the dangers of distracted driving in today's road traffic environment.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, Ask Insurance Agent for an insurance fact
Alexa, Ask Insurance Agent to tell me something
Alexa, Ask insurance Agent to give me trivia
name: Car Insurance Facts
shortDescription: Car Insurance facts that outline coverage, discounts and dangers
